## GetItem for a project's image processing status.
## Uses the projectId path parameter to look up the project record.
## Only needs the imageProcessed field, but GetItem returns the whole item.
## Auth: Cognito (enforced at the method level, not in VTL).
{
  "TableName": "$stageVariables.tableName",
  "Key": {
    "PK": { "S": "PROJECT#$input.params('projectId')" },
    "SK": { "S": "PROJECT#$input.params('projectId')" }
  }
}
